{["next"]={1736},area="Himbar",zone="Angmar",reputation={{val="+500 with Council of the North"}},money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Himbar is haunted by the merrevail and their kindred, the bats. These creatures prey upon the Rangers of Gath Forthnír, showing no mercy.",mobs={{locations={"10.90N, 23.93W","10.89N, 23.93W"},name="Thoriel"}},category="Angmar",id=627,scope="n/a",t="Small Fellowship",prev={2646},name="Cries of the Host",arcs="Winged Host",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Thoriel",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe merrevail hunt throughout Himbar, the lands west of Gath Forthnír.\nThoriel has asked you to remove the lieutenant, Iarvael, from the morroval caverns.\n* Kill 1 Iarvael\nObj 2:\nThoriel waits for you in Gath Forthnír, the hidden Ranger-camp east of Himbar.\nYou have defeated Iorvael and should now return to Thoriel with news of your victory.\n* Talk to Thoriel"},
