{["next"]={2698},reputation={{val="+1200 with The Wardens of Annúminas"}},money={{val="18s 90c"}},d="With the ropes strung you can now make your way to the peak of the colossus and survey all of Evendim.",selectoneof={{val="Scarred Shield of the Dunedain",id="700264F0"},{val="Shield of the Northern Healers",id=70026275},{val="Battered Dunedain Defender's Shield",id="7002619E"},{val="Shield of the Vigilant Sentry",id="70025FBD"}},category="Evendim",id=629,scope="n/a",prev={697},name="Crown of the Colossus",receive={{q="(x3)",val="Silver Arnorian Coin",id="7002663E"}},level=33,minlevel=28,b="Sardan",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe rope to climb the colossus is nearby.\nMake your way to the top of the colossus and have a look.\n* Have a look around (Perform /look)\n* Climb the peak of the colossus\nObj 2:\nSardan is at the base of the colossus.\nSardan will be interested to hear what you have seen.\n* Talk to Sardan near the colossus"},
