{reputation={{val="+900 with The Wardens of Annúminas"}},zone="Evendim",area="Tyrn Fornech",money={{val="19s 60c"}},d="The tomb-robbers are killing elk and bear for food, cutting into the supply Ost Forod will need to survive the coming winter.",mobs={{locations={"8.01S, 64.59W"},name="Clark Standish"}},category="Evendim",id=1803,scope="n/a",name="Robbers and Poachers",receive={{q="(x2)",val="Bronze Arnorian Coin",id="7002663D"}},level=35,minlevel=30,b="Clark Standish",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nTomb-robbers can be found in the hills north and east of Ost Forod.\nClark Standish asked you to venture into the hills around Ost Forod and defeat several tomb-robbers to protect the town's winter food-supply.\n* Defeat tomb-robbers around Ost Forod (10)\nObj 2:\nClark Standish is at Ost Forod.\nClark Standish will be pleased to know that the tomb-robbers have several fewer mouths to feed.\n* Talk to Clark Standish at Ost Forod",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
