{["next"]={1571},area="Buckland",zone="Bree-land",d="Rollo Maggot, one of Farmer Maggot's sons, has gone missing, and Wilmar Brandybuck, Maggot's farmhand is worried.",mobs={{locations={"31.64S, 62.58W"},name="Wilmac Brandybuck"},{locations={"33.34S, 62.41W"},name="Saradoc Brandybuck"}},category="Bree-land",id=1813,scope="n/a",prev={2788},name="Rollo and Doderic",arcs="Old Forestry",level=15,minlevel=11,b="Wilmac Brandybuck",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nSaradoc Brandybuck can be found at Brandy Hall at the centre of Buckland, south of the Buckland Gate.\nWilmac Brandybuck has asked you to find Farmer Maggot's son Rollo. He suggested that Rollo may be off gallivanting with his friend Doderic Brandybuck, and that Doderic's uncle, Saradoc, may know where they are.\n* Talk to Saradoc Brandybuck at Brandy Hall",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
