{["next"]={1861},reputation={{val="+900 with The Wardens of Annúminas"}},money={{val="18s 90c"}},d="Adleithian is concerned that tomb-robbers have taken control of the ruins of Barad Tharsír in the Barandalf.",category="Evendim",id=1851,scope="n/a",name="Scavengers of Barad Tharsír",receive={{q="(x2)",val="Bronze Arnorian Coin",id="7002663D"}},level=33,minlevel=28,b="Adleithian",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nBarad Tharsír is located south-east of the Colossus, in the Barandalf, on the far side of the Brandywine.\nAdleithian has asked you to defeat members of the robber-band that has taken Barad Tharsír.\n* Defeat tomb-robbers at Barad Tharsír (12)\nObj 2:\nAdleithian is at the Ranger camp at the Colossus, north-west of the Barandalf and west of Parth Aduial.\nAdleithian is waiting to hear that you have defeated the robbers at Barad Tharsír.\n* Talk to Adleithian",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
