\nNathronwen is at Duillond, the Refuge in Ered Luin.\nScholar Nathronwen has asked you to compose a Ballad of Aiglos for her to judge so she may evaluate your own progress as a scholar.\n* Bring the Ballad of Aiglos to Nathronwen\n* Turn in Ballad of Aiglos (Level 15)",traits={{val="Journeyman Scholar Proficiency"}},faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
