nd next to Jalmari in Sûri-kylä.\nJalmari has instructed you to use wisdom in ordering certain items off import to the Lossoth. He told you the following in regard to the items:\n'Warmth is of great importance in these frozen lands, so fire is a boon companion. Even more important is water, for without water there is no life.\n'Even with fire and water at your disposal, these lands are not safe. A wise person will take with him stout weapons to protect himself, though he must first have food enough to lend himself the strength to wield such weapons.\n'Above all, a wanderer in these lands must have clothing warm enough to protect him against the cold when fire cannot be made.'\n* Use Weapons\nObj 7:\nJalmari is at Sûri-kylä near to the steam-lodge.\nYou should return to Jalmari with the solution to his puzzle.\n* Talk to Jalmari",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={2967},reputation={{val="+500 with Lossoth of Forochel"}},zone="Forochel",area="Jä-rannit",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="You completed three tasks given you by the Lossoth people, earning their favour and the right to speak with Yrjänä.",mobs={{locations={"19.54N, 71.99W"},name="Yrjänä"}},selectoneof={{val="Jacket of Kestoaika",id="700105F2"},{val="Breastplate of Voima",id="700105F1"},{val="Robe of Viisaus",id="700105F0"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2808,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2964},name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 4: The Hand of Angmar",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Yrjänä",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nYrjänä is in the Great Lodge of Sûri-kylä.\nYrjänä informed you that another has come claiming Narchuil and seeking the aid of the Lossoth in finding it.\n* Go with Yrjänä to meet your rival\nObj 2:\nYrjänä is in the Great Lodge of Sûri-kylä.\nYou should speak with Yrjänä regarding Mordrambor's threats.\n* Talk to Yrjänä"},
{["next"]={2968},zone="Forochel",area="Jä-rannit",d="The Black Númenórean Mordrambor arrived at the Lossoth village demanding the loyalty of the Lossoth people, striking fear into their hearts.",mobs={{locations={"19.54N, 71.99W"},name="Yrjänä"},{locations={"20.05N, 78.34W","20.63N, 84.69W"},name="Saija"},{locations={"18.77N, 81.29W"},name="Arvedui"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2809,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2966},name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 5: The Myth of the Monster",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Yrjänä",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nSaija is at Näky-kolo north west of Kuru-leiri.\nYrjänä instructed you to seek the wisdom of Saija in order to find Narchuil.\n* Talk to Saija\nObj 2:\nThe body of the sea-monster Saija spoke of lies in the Ice-bay of Forochel, east of Kuru-leiri.\nSaija directed you to seek Narchuil or news of it upon the body of a sea-monster which can be seen in the Ice-bay of Forochel.\n* Seek the body of the sea-monster in the Ice-bay of Forochel\nObj 3:\nArvedui haunts the wreckage of a great Elf-ship frozen in the Ice-bay of Forochel.\nYou have discovered the shade of Arvedui, the last king of Arthedain, haunting the wreckage of the Elf-ship which had come to rescue him so long ago. It may be that the shade will know the whereabouts of Narchuil.\n* Talk to Arvedui",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={2969},zone="Forochel",area="Talvi-mûri",d="Upon finding the wreckage of the ship which came to carry King Arvedui back to the Grey Havens, you made an even more shocking discovery: the shade of Arvedui himself.",mobs={{locations={"19.02N, 70.79W"},name="Lothrandir"},{locations={"18.77N, 81.29W"},name="Arvedui"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2810,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2967},name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 6: The Dwarf-mines",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Arvedui",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe book of heraldry lies in the dwarf-mines where Arvedui and his people hid in Länsi-mâ.\nArvedui instructed you to find the book of heraldry that was abandoned deep in the old dwarf-mines and bring it to a Ranger encamped in Forochel.\n* Turn in Book of Heraldry\nObj 2:\nThe Ranger is encamped at Sûri-kylä.\nNow that you have found the book of heraldry as directed by Arvedui, you should take it to the Ranger the ancient king spoke of.\n* Talk to Lothrandir\n* Turn in Book of Heraldry\nObj 3:\nArevedui is in the wreckage of the Elf-ship, north along the Ice-bay in Talvi-mûri.\nHaving delivered the book, you should return to Arvedui for further guidance.\n* Talk to Arvedui",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={2970},zone="Forochel",area="Talvi-mûri",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="To gain the trust of Arvedui's restless spirit, you have performed a deed of kindness for him and delivered a lost tome to one of the descendants of his house.",mobs={{locations={"20.05N, 78.34W","20.63N, 84.69W"},name="Saija"},{locations={"18.77N, 81.29W"},name="Arvedui"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2811,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2968},name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 7: The Lost Mariner",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Arvedui",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nSaija is at Näky-kolo north west of Kuru-leiri.\nArvedui told you that the captain of the Elf-ship did not perish with his vessel and suggested that you seek the knowledge of Saija regarding the fate of Aearil and his crew.\n* Talk to Saija"},
{["next"]={2973},zone="Forochel",area="Talvi-mûri",money={{val="39s 76c"}},d="Not only did you find the wreckage of the Elf-ship which had borne King Arvedui from the shores of Forochel, but you found the shade of Arvedui himself.",mobs={{locations={"20.05N, 78.34W","20.63N, 84.69W"},name="Saija"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2812,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2969},name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 8: A Dark Storm",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Saija",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nSaija is at Näky-kolo north west of Kuru-leiri.\nSaija will tell you what you need to know, but wants you to perform two tasks for her.\nObj 2:\nSaija is at Näky-kolo north west of Kuru-leiri.\nNow that you have completed both of the tasks she set before you, you should speak again with Saija.\n* Talk to Saija"},
{reputation={{val="+700 with Lossoth of Forochel"}},zone="Forochel",area="Talvi-mûri",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Saija has two tasks she requires of you before she imparts her knowledge.",mobs={{locations={"20.05N, 78.34W","20.63N, 84.69W"},name="Saija"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2813,scope="Epic",t="Epic",name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 8: A Test of the Cold",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Saija",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nIce-giants can be found south and west of Näky-kolo.\nSaija has tasked you with defeating the Ice-giants that have come down from the mountains.  She also suggests pulling them onto hot springs to weaken them.\n* Defeat Ice-giants  (10)\nObj 2:\nSaija is at Näky-kolo north west of Kuru-leiri.\nHaving defeated the Ice-giants, you should return at once to Saija.\n* Talk to Saija",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{reputation={{val="+700 with Lossoth of Forochel"}},zone="Forochel",area="Talvi-mûri",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Saija has two tasks she requires of you before she imparts her knowledge.",mobs={{locations={"20.05N, 78.34W","20.63N, 84.69W"},name="Saija"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2814,scope="Epic",t="Epic",name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 8: Spirits of Angmar",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Saija",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nIce-wights can be found above Näky-kolo south and west from Näky-kolo.\nSaija has tasked you with banishing the Ice-wights from the shores of Forochel.\n* Defeat Ice-wights (10)\nObj 2:\nSaija is at Näky-kolo.\nNow that you have defeated many Ice-wights, you should return to Saija as instructed.\n* Talk to Saija",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={1134,2974},zone="Forochel",area="Talvi-mûri",money={{val="39s 76c"}},d="Saija disclosed to you the location of a cave where the Lossoth believe the captain of the second Elf-ship may have taken refuge after the ship was sunk.",mobs={{locations={"20.05N, 78.34W","20.63N, 84.69W"},name="Saija"},{locations={"18.77N, 81.29W"},name="Arvedui"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2815,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2970},name="Vol. I, Book 13, Chapter 9: The Path of Aearil",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Saija",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe Elf-captain or his belongings may remain within the cave.\nSaija suggested you speak with her again to seek out the cave, and she would guide you there.\nThis quest is meant for a fellowship. If you choose to undertake this quest solo you will receive an inspiration bonus, but the challenge will be great.\n* Find Narchuil\nObj 2:\nThe shade of Arvedui is at the Ruin of Thoroval north and east along the Ice Bay in Talvi-mûri.\nHaving recovered a ring-fragment from Aearil's belongings, you should seek out the shade of Arvedui and let him know the fate of his would-be rescuer and learn whether the fragment you found is indeed the lost half of Narchuil.\n* Talk to Arvedui\n* Turn in Half of the ring Narchuil (Level 1)"},
{zone="Forochel",area="Jä-rannit",d="Yrjänä told you that the Angmarim have also come to Sûri-kylä, led by a Black Númenórean.",mobs={{locations={"19.51N, 71.98W"},name="Yrjänä"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2816,scope="n/a",t="Epic",name="Vol. I, Book 13, Instance: The Hand of Angmar",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nAccompany Yrjänä to meet with the emissary of Angmar.\n* Talk to Yrjänä\nObj 2:\nYrjänä and the Elders of the Lossoth are to meet with the emissary from Angmar.",faction="FrP",instanced="Yes"},
{d="Saija has promised to guide you in your search for Narchuil.",category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",id=2817,scope="n/a",t="Epic",name="Vol. I, Book 13, Instance:  The Path of Aearil",arcs="Volume I, Book 13: Doom of the Last-king",level=50,minlevel=45,repeatable="No",instanced="Yes",faction="FrP",o="Obj 1:\nSpeak to Saija inside of Halla-kolo.\n* Talk to Saija\nObj 2:\nSearch Halla-kolo for the ring Narchuil.\n* Search for Narchuil\nObj 3:\nSearch Halla-kolo for the ring Narchuil.\n* Use Ancient Chest"},
{["next"]={2991},zone="Bree-land",area="Bree",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Newbold Leafcutter directed you to the tomb of Maenadar the Craftsman, but you came too late to recover Celebrimbor's shaping tool.",mobs={{locations={"30.40S, 51.71W","64.80N, 133.31W","30.47S, 51.65W","64.73N, 133.25W"},name="Newbold Leafcutter"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2818,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2989},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 10: Trailing Angmar",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Newbold Leafcutter",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nEglamír is at Celondim in Ered Luin, far to the west of Bree-land.\nNewbold Leafcutter suggested you return to Eglamír for more advice.\n* Talk to Eglamír at Celondim"},
{["next"]={2992},zone="Forochel",area="Jä-rannit",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Newbold Leafcutter could help you no longer and suggested you return to Eglamír at Celondim.",mobs={{locations={"19.54N, 71.99W"},name="Yrjänä"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2819,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2990},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 11: The Great Bellows of Mirobel",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Eglamír",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nYrjänä is at Sûri-kylä in Forochel, far to the east and north of Celondim.\nEglamír believes that Amarthiel's minions may be trying to find the lair of a dragon which may still dwell in Forochel, the hide from which may be used to repair the bellows of the forges at Mirobel. He suggests you go to the frozen north and speak with the Lossoth chieftain Yrjänä.\n* Talk to Yrjänä at Sûri-kylä"},
{["next"]={2993,1136},reputation={{val="+900 with Lossoth of Forochel"}},zone="Forochel",area="Jä-rannit",money={{val="49s 70c"}},d="Eglamír believes that the minions of Amarthiel may be seeking the hide of the Dragon of Forochel to repair the great bellows of Mirobel, the Ring-forges of Eregion, and sent you to learn of Bregmor for Yrjänä, the chieftain of Sûri-kylä.",mobs={{locations={"19.54N, 71.99W"},name="Yrjänä"}},selectoneof={{val="Bregmor's Woe",id="700108AD"},{val="Bregmor's Fall",id="700108AC"},{val="Bregmor's Bane",id="700108A5"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2820,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2991},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 12: Skin of Bregmor",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Yrjänä",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nBregmor's lair can be found far to the west of Sûri-kylä, south-east of Jotunstath.\nYrjänä told you that the dragon Bregmor once terrorized Forochel, but no longer. He also indicated that he would not spare his people to guide you to Bregmor's lair, leaving you to fend for yourself.\nThis quest is meant for a fellowship. If you choose to undertake this quest solo you will receive an inspiration bonus, but the challenge will be great.\n* Find and enter Bregmor's lair\nObj 2:\nYrjänä is at Sûri-kylä, far to the east of Bregmor's lair.\nYou failed to stop Angmar from obtaining the hide of the dragon Bregmor and should now return to Yrjänä with your news.\n* Talk to Yrjänä at Sûri-kylä"},
{["next"]={2994},zone="Forochel",area="Jä-rannit",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="You failed to stop the machinations of Angmar in Forochel, leaving the servants of Amarthiel free to rekindle the forges of Mirobel.",mobs={{locations={"19.54N, 71.99W"},name="Yrjänä"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2821,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2992},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 13: Frustrated Hopes",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Yrjänä",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nEglamír is at Celondim in Ered Luin, far to the south and west of Forochel.\nYrjänä told you to return to Eglamír with news of your failure.\n* Talk to Eglamír at Celondim"},
{["next"]={2995},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="With hide from the dragon Bregmor and Celebrimbor's shaping tool, there is nothing more Eglamír knows of that Amarthiel will need to rekindle the forges of Eregion and reforge Narchuil.",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2822,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2993},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 14: The Heavy Burden",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Eglamír",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nElrond is at Rivendell in the Trollshaws, far to the east of Celondim.\nEglamír suggested that you bring news of your failure to Elrond at Rivendell.\n* Talk to Elrond at Rivendell"},
{["next"]={2996,1137},reputation={{val="+900 with Elves of Rivendell"}},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="49s 70c"}},d="With your defeats in Bree-land and Forochel, little remains now but to throw yourself at Amarthiel's forces in a vain attempt to put an end to her plans.",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},selectoneof={{val="Tathredhranc",id="700108B2"},{val="Luth-herthar",id="700108AE"},{val="Hadoranc",id="700108A6"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2823,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2994},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 15: The Doom of the North",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Elrond",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nMirobel can be reached by travelling far to the south, into the land of Eregion.\nElrond instructed you to journey to Mirobel and do whatever you can to stop Amarthiel.\nThis quest is meant for a fellowship. If you choose to undertake this quest solo you will receive an inspiration bonus, but the challenge will be great.\n* Travel to Mirobel and try to stop Amarthiel\nObj 2:\nThe watch-captain Glorenthol is at Delossad in Tâl Bruinen.\nYou failed to stop Amarthiel, but she was at last defeated at the surprise return of Mordirith. Narchuil has fallen into the hands of the False King, but Amarthiel is now the prisoner of the Free Peoples. You should speak with the watch-captain Glorenthol.\n* Talk to the watch-captain\nObj 3:\nElrond is in his library at the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nThe watch-captain has directed you to speak with Elrond regarding your mission to Mirobel.\n* Talk to Elrond at Rivendell"},
{zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Laerdan sent you to Filegnaneth to collect provisions for the journey to Eregion, but she does not have the fine clover honey she requires to make lembas, the waybread of the Elves.",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Filegnaneth"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2824,scope="Epic",t="Epic",name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 1: Many Provisions",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Filegnaneth",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe expert cook is in Michel Delving in the Shire, far to the west of Rivendell. Filegnaneth is at Rivendell in the Trollshaws, far to the east of the Shire.\nFilegnaneth has asked you to travel to the Shire and purchase fine clover honey from the expert cook there.\n* Bring the fine clover honey to Filegnaneth\n* Turn in Drop of Fine Clover Honey",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={1135},reputation={{val="+500 with Council of the North"}},zone="Angmar",area="Himbar",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Laerdan sent you to Gath Forthnír to reclaim his breastplate from the Ranger Golodir.",mobs={{locations={"10.90N, 23.93W","10.89N, 23.93W"},name="Golodir"}},selectoneof={{val="Golodir's Cloak",id="700108A9"},{val="Golodir's Wrap",id="700108B3"},{val="Golodir's Mantle",id="700108A8"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2825,scope="Epic",t="Epic",name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 1: The Heraldry of Lindon",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Golodir",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nDolendath is located in Imlad Balchorth, south and west of Myrkworth.\nGolodir suggested that you may find Laerdan's breastplate at Dolendath, the place where Golodir's army first took refuge in Angmar.\nThis quest is meant for a fellowship. If you choose to undertake this quest solo you will receive an inspiration bonus, but the challenge will be great.\n* Bring Laerdan's breastplate back to Golodir at Gath Forthnír\n* Turn in Elf-breastplate"},
{["next"]={2982},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Laerdan is preparing to make the journey to Eregion, but he needs your aid to finish his preparations.",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"},{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Laerdan"}},selectoneof={{val="Laerdan's Quill",id="700108A3"},{val="Laerdan's Note",id="700108AB"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2826,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2975},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 1: The Long Road South",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,c={"* Golodir at Gath Forthnír (leads to Chapter 1: The Heraldry of Lindon)\n* Filegnaneth in the Hall of Fire of the Last Homely House (leads to Chapter 1: Many Provisions)\n* Nat Collop, the Stable-master at Tinnudir in Evendim (leads to Chapter 1: The Steed Arel)"},pois={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Laerdan's Note"}},minlevel=45,b="Laerdan",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nFilegnaneth is found in the Hall of Fire at Rivendell. Nat Collop is found in Tinnudír in Evendim, far to the west and north of the Trollshaws. Golodir is found in Gath Forthnír in Angmar, far to the north of the Trollshaws.\nLaerdan asked you to perform several tasks on his behalf.\n* Talk to Filegnaneth in Rivendell\n* Talk to Nat Collop at Tinnudír\n* Talk to Golodir at Gath Forthnír\nObj 2:\nLaerdan is at the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nYou should return at once to Laerdan with news of your successes, but also of the resulting delays.\n* Find/Use Laerdan's Note\nObj 3:\nElrond is in his library in the Last Homely House at Rivendell.\nYou should tell Elrond of Laerdan's note at once.\n* Talk to Elrond in Rivendell"},
{zone="Evendim",area="Parth Aduial",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Laerdan has asked you to speak with Nat Collop, a Man of Ost Forod who oversees the stable at Tinnudír, about sending his horse, Arel, to Rivendell.",mobs={{locations={"12.35S, 67.18W"},name="Nat Collop"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2827,scope="Epic",t="Epic",name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 1: The Steed Arel",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Nat Collop",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nThorin's Hall is in Ered Luin, far to the west and south of Evendim.\nNat Collop has asked you to speak with the expert metalsmith at Thorin's Hall and obtain some dwarf-steel cutlery moulds.\n* Bring the dwarf-steel cutlery moulds to Nat Collop at Tinnudír\n* Turn in Dwarf-steel Cutlery Mould",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={2983},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="You found a note left by Laerdan indicating that he has left Rivendell with the intent of bringing the shards of Narchuil to Amarthiel.",mobs={{locations={"29.30S, 6.72W"},name="Ladrochan"},{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2828,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2980},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 2: Laerdan's Trail",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Elrond",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nLadrochan, the Stable-master, can be found in the stables of Rivendell, west of the Last Homely House.\nElrond has told you to speak with Ladrochan and learn how long ago Laerdan left Rivendell.\n* Talk to Ladrochan at the stable in Rivendell\nObj 2:\nElrond is in his library in the Last Homely House of Rivendell, to the east of the stable.\nLadrochan told you that Laerdan had left Rivendell two days ago. You should return to Elrond with this news at once.\n* Talk to Elrond in Rivendell"},
{["next"]={2984},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Elrond was dismayed by Laerdan's secret departure. Doubts have been cast now upon the honour of the Elf-lord, and Elrond desires to know the truth behind his disappearance.",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2829,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2982},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 3: Shedding Light",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Elrond",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nLaerdan's room is in the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nElrond has asked you to search Laerdan's rooms for anything which might reveal Laerdan's full purpose.\n* Find/Use Coil of Rope\n* Find/Use Pack\n* Find/Use Map of Eregion\nObj 2:\nElrond is in the library at the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nYou found a journal in Laerdan's rooms. It may reveal Laerdan's plans.\n* Examine Laerdan's journal"},
{["next"]={2985},reputation={{val="+300 with Elves of Rivendell"}},money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="While searching Laerdan's rooms, you discovered his journal, the passage he had read last marked clearly.",selectoneof={{val="Elechor",id="700108B0"},{val="Belegechor",id="700108AA"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2830,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2983},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 4: The Prisoner of Sammath Baul",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Laerdan's Journal",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nYou should read further into the journal...it may provide some clues as to Laerdan's purposes.\n* Read Laerdan's journal further\nObj 2:\nWhile reading Laerdan's journal, you discover that Laerdan believes he saw his daughter Narmeleth there at Sammath Baul. This entry is quite disturbing....\n* Finish reading the journal"},
{["next"]={2986},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Laerdan's journal contained a horrid description of his imprisonment and torture at Sammath Baul.",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2831,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2984},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 5: Laerdan's Fall",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Laerdan's Journal",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nElrond is found in the Library of the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nYou should return at once to Elrond and tell him what you have learned.\n* Talk to Elrond"},
{["next"]={2987},reputation={{val="+300 with Elves of Rivendell"}},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Elrond was alarmed by the journal entry you described, fearing the worst for Laerdan.",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},selectoneof={{val="Golechor",id="700108AF"},{val="Torechor",id="700108A4"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2832,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2985},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 6: The Fate of Laerdan",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Elrond",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nElrond is in his library at the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nElrond wishes to speak with you regarding what he discovered in Laerdan's journal.\n* Discuss with Elrond what fate may await Laerdan\nObj 2:\nElrond is in his library at the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nYou discussed the fate of Laerdan with Elrond, coming to a dire conclusion.\n* Talk to Elrond"},
{["next"]={2988},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="Laerdan's journal brings more concerns upon Elrond than just the fate of Laerdan....",mobs={{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2833,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2986},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 7: The Ravages of Time",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Elrond",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nElrond spoke of an Elf named Eglamír who may dwell in Celondim in Ered Luin, far to the west of Rivendell and the Trollshaws.\nElrond has told you that Celebrimbor wisely did not record many of the details of Ring-craft in the lore of Eregion. However Elrond did find many references to an Elf named Eglamír who may know more.\n* Search for Eglamír in Celondim"},
{["next"]={2989},zone="Bree-land",area="Bree",money={{val="24s 85c"}},d="In an effort to learn more of the Ring-lore of Eregion, Elrond sent you to Eglamír, an Elf of Eregion who dwells now at Celondim.",mobs={{locations={"30.40S, 51.71W","64.80N, 133.31W","30.47S, 51.65W","64.73N, 133.25W"},name="Newbold Leafcutter"},{locations={"29.60S, 51.25W","29.64S, 51.28W","29.61S, 51.26W","29.53S, 51.29W"},name="Barliman Butterbur"},{locations={"31.08S, 51.24W","31.08S, 51.25W"},name="Mayor Graeme Tenderlarch"},{locations={"28.16S, 53.33W"},name="Chief Watcher Grimbriar"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2834,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2987},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 8: An Elf-friend of Eregion",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,minlevel=45,b="Eglamír",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nBree-town lies in Bree-land, far to the east of Ered Luin.\nEglamír would speak little of the Ring-lore of Eregion, but did tell you that the Ring-smith Celebrimbor gave a shaping tool to a Man of Bree-land. He suggests you find someone in Bree who might know the whereabouts of the Man's barrow.\n* Talk to Barliman Butterbur\n* Talk to Chief Watcher Grimbriar\n* Talk to Mayor Graeme Tenderlarch\nObj 2:\nNewbold Leafcutter can be found at the Scholar's Stairs Archive in Bree-town.\nYou were advised to seek out Newbold Leafcutter to learn more regarding the whereabouts of Celebrimbor's shaping tool.\n* Talk to Newbold Leafcutter"},
{["next"]={2990},reputation={{val="+700 with Men of Bree"}},zone="Bree-land",area="Bree",money={{val="49s 70c"}},d="Eglamír sent you in search of someone with knowledge of the Barrow-downs and the shaping tool of Celebrimbor.",mobs={{locations={"30.40S, 51.71W","64.80N, 133.31W","30.47S, 51.65W","64.73N, 133.25W"},name="Newbold Leafcutter"}},selectoneof={{val="Leafcutter's Buckler",id="700108A7"},{val="Leafcutter's Targe",id="700187A8"},{val="Leafcutter's Shield",id="700108B1"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",id=2835,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2988},name="Vol. I, Book 14, Chapter 9: The Barrows of Haudh Iarchith",arcs="Volume I, Book 14: The Ring-forges of Eregion",level=50,pois={{locations={"35.10S, 55.28W","41.80N, 146.11W"},name="Maenadar's Crypt"}},minlevel=45,b="Newbold Leafcutter",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe tomb of Maenadar can be found in the small barrow beside the entrance to Haudh Iarchith in the southern parts of the Barrow-downs.\nNewbold Leafcutter told you that the shaping tool can be found in the tomb of Maenadar the Craftsman.\n* Find the tomb of Maenadar the Craftsman\nObj 2:\nNewbold Leafcutter is at the Scholar's Stairs Archive in Bree-town.\nYou came too late to the tomb of Maenadar and found it despoiled. Angmar arrived first. You should return to Newbold Leafcutter to learn if he knows anything else.\n* Talk to Newbold Leafcutter in Bree"},
{["next"]={3006},zone="Angmar",area="Himbar",money={{val="10s 8c"}},d="Narmeleth believes she knows the secret to Mordirith's weakness.",mobs={{locations={"10.90N, 23.93W","10.89N, 23.93W"},name="Golodir"},{locations={"10.90N, 23.93W","10.89N, 23.93W"},name="Narmeleth"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2836,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={3004},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 10: The Broken Blade of Dúnachar",level=51,minlevel=46,b="Golodir",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nNarmeleth is in her father's old room at Gath Forthnír in the northern reaches of Angmar.\nNarmeleth has told you to speak with Golodir and find what has become of the broken blade of Dúnachar.\n* Talk to Narmeleth at Gath Forthnír\nObj 2:\nGolodir is in his room in Gath Forthnír.\nNarmeleth has told you to speak with Golodir and find what has become of the broken blade of Dúnachar.\n* Talk to Golodir",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={3007},zone="Angmar",area="Himbar",money={{val="25s 20c"}},d="Narmeleth believes that baring the shattered hilt of Dúnachar before Mordirith will weaken the False King's will.",mobs={{locations={"10.90N, 23.93W","10.89N, 23.93W"},name="Golodir"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2837,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={3005},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 11: A Father's Final Gift",level=51,pois={{locations={"4.21N, 22.43W"},name="Burial Mound"}},minlevel=46,b="Golodir",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nLorniel's grave is on the northern slopes of Gorothlad, south of Nan Gurth in Angmar.\nGolodir has given you the location of Dúnachar and has given you permission to retrieve it.\n* Use Burial Mound\nObj 2:\nGolodir is at Gath Forthnír in the northern reaches of Angmar.\nYou should return to Golodir with the broken hilt of Dúnachar.\n* Talk to Golodir\n* Turn in Hilt of Dúnachar",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={3180},zone="Angmar",area="Himbar",money={{val="51s 10c"}},d="Narmeleth seeks to put a final end to Mordrambor and Mordirith.",mobs={{locations={"10.90N, 23.93W","10.89N, 23.93W"},name="Golodir"},{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Failloth"},{locations={"10.90N, 23.93W","10.89N, 23.93W"},name="Narmeleth"},{locations={"30.14S, 3.06W"},name="Glorfindel"},{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},selectoneof={{val="Golodir's Boon",id=70018766},{val="Golodir's Offering",id=70018765},{val="Golodir's Gift",id=70018764}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2838,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={3006},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 12: One Hope Remains",receive={{val="Narmeleth's Legacy",id=70018768}},level=52,minlevel=47,b="Golodir",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nGath Forthnír is in the northern reaches of Angmar.\nGolodir told you to bring the hilt to Narmeleth in Gath Forthnír.\nThis quest is meant for a fellowship. If you choose to undertake this quest solo you will receive an inspiration bonus, but the challenge will be great.\n* Talk to Narmeleth\n* Turn in Hilt of Dúnachar\nObj 2:\nNarmeleth is in Gath Forthnír in the northern reaches of Angmar.\nNarmeleth told you to gather friends and speak with her again to begin the final assault.\nThis quest is meant for a fellowship. If you choose to undertake this quest solo you will receive an inspiration bonus, but the challenge will be great.\n* Assault Gador Gúlaran\nObj 3:\nGath Forthnír is in the northern reaches of Angmar.\nYou should speak with Golodir in Gath Forthnír.\n* Talk to Golodir at Gath Forthnír\nObj 4:\nRivendell is in the north-east corner of the Trollshaws.\nGolodir sent you to speak with Glorfindel and bring him news of Mordirith's defeat.\n* Talk to Glorfindel in Rivendell\nObj 5:\nElrond can be found in the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nGlorfindel told you to deliver your tidings to Master Elrond.\n* Talk to Elrond in Rivendell\nObj 6:\nFailloth is in the courtyard of the Last Homely House in Rivendell.\nElrond told you to retrieve Laerdan's legacy from Failloth, the caretakers of Rivendell.\n* Talk to Failloth in Rivendell"},
{["next"]={2997},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Rivendell Valley",money={{val="25s 20c"}},d="Elrond shares your concerns about Amarthiel and has asked Lord Glorfindel to deal with the matter.",mobs={{locations={"38.62S, 12.63W"},name="Narmeleth"},{locations={"30.14S, 3.06W"},name="Glorfindel"},{locations={"29.77S, 3.38W","29.59S, 3.10W","29.60S, 3.10W"},name="Elrond"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2839,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2995},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 1: A Strange Fate",level=51,minlevel=46,b="Elrond",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nGlorfindel can be found outside the Last Homely House to the south-east, looking out on the Falls of Imladris.\nElrond has asked you to speak with Glorfindel.\n* Talk to Glorfindel in Rivendell\nObj 2:\nDelossad is south-west of Rivendell in Tâl Bruinen, east of Garbert's cottage.\nGlorfindel has asked that you question Narmeleth in Delossad.\n* Talk to Narmeleth at Delossad",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={2998},zone="The Trollshaws",area="Tâl Bruinen",money={{val="25s 20c"}},d="Narmeleth has turned from her evil ways and has offered her knowledge in aid of the Free Peoples.",mobs={{locations={"9.39S, 41.16W","9.40S, 41.16W","9.60S, 41.05W"},name="Halbarad"},{locations={"38.62S, 12.63W"},name="Narmeleth"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2840,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2996},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 2: A Threat to the Dúnedain",level=51,minlevel=46,b="Narmeleth",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nEsteldín is in the North Downs, a land north-west of the Trollshaws.\nNarmeleth wishes for you to travel to Esteldín and warn Halbarad of the spy.\n* Talk to Halbarad at Esteldín",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={2999},zone="The North Downs",area="Esteldín",money={{val="10s 8c"}},d="You must help prove that Narmeleth is telling the truth by questioning refugees from Angmar.",mobs={{locations={"9.39S, 41.16W","9.40S, 41.16W","9.60S, 41.05W"},name="Halbarad"},{locations={"9.72S, 41.36W"},name="Rhona"},{locations={"9.65S, 40.52W"},name="Nairnë"},{locations={"9.63S, 41.06W"},name="Eón"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2841,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2997},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 3: Proof's Burden",level=51,minlevel=46,b="Halbarad",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe refugees are outside of the library, near the craft-hall, watching the Rangers train, and by the stable-master in Esteldín.\nHalbarad is not convinced of Narmeleth's intentions, but has allowed you to question the Hillman-refugees from Angmar.\n* Talk to Nairnë\n* Talk to Eón\n* Talk to Rhona\nObj 2:\nHalbarad is in Esteldín in the North Downs.\nYou should return to Halbarad and inform him that one of the refugees is missing.\n* Talk to Halbarad at Esteldín",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
{["next"]={3000},zone="The North Downs",area="Esteldín",money={{val="25s 20c"}},d="Halbarad has asked that you find the missing refugee and bring her back to Esteldín.",mobs={{locations={"9.39S, 41.16W","9.40S, 41.16W","9.60S, 41.05W"},name="Halbarad"}},selectoneof={{val="Halbarad's Trust",id=70018767},{val="Protector of Esteldín",id=70018769}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2842,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2998},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 4: Esteldín's Fate",level=51,minlevel=46,b="Halbarad",repeatable="No",faction="FrP",instanced="No",o="Obj 1:\nThe missing refugee might be found in the eastern-most pass between the North Downs and Angmar.\nHalbarad instructed you to search for signs of the missing refugee.\n* Find the missing refugee\nObj 2:\nHalbarad is in Esteldín in the North Downs.\nYou should return to Halbarad and inform him that the refugee was a spy.\n* Talk to Halbarad at Esteldín"},
{["next"]={3001},zone="The North Downs",area="Esteldín",money={{val="25s 20c"}},d="Narmeleth's warning about the spy proved true and proved her good intentions to Halbarad.",mobs={{locations={"9.39S, 41.16W","9.40S, 41.16W","9.60S, 41.05W"},name="Halbarad"},{locations={"38.62S, 12.63W"},name="Narmeleth"}},category="Epic - Vol. I, Book 15: Daughter of Strife",id=2843,scope="Epic",t="Epic",prev={2999},name="Vol. I, Book 15, Chapter 5: The Ring of Truth",level=51,minlevel=46,b="Halbarad",repeatable="No",o="Obj 1:\nNarmeleth is at Delossad in Tâl Bruinen.\nHalbarad has asked that you bring his thanks to Narmeleth for her aid in saving Esteldín.\n* Talk to Narmeleth at Delossad",faction="FrP",instanced="No"},
